    <item>
      <title>米莱希望阿根廷人为他实现经济美元化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/milei-wants-argentines-to-dollarize-the-economy-for-him-shock-therapy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈维尔·米莱伊似乎已经放弃了阿根廷经济突然正式美元化的愿景。这位政治家在去年的总统竞选期间曾建议炸毁央行的比索印钞机，但现在他不再谈论这件事了。相反，他希望他的同胞为他完成这项工作。一美元一美元，一比索一比索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/milei-wants-argentines-to-dollarize-the-economy-for-him-shock-therapy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 14:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙称过度监管将使欧洲落后于美国和中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/macron-warns-that-eu-needs-radical-change-is-lagging-china-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙对欧盟前景表示悲观，他警告称，缺乏投资和过多的监管将使欧盟缺乏竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/macron-warns-that-eu-needs-radical-change-is-lagging-china-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:59:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
