    <item>
      <title>法国计划在 2025 年削减 600 亿欧元支出并提高税收</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/france-plans-66-billion-in-spending-cuts-and-tax-hikes-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 寻求收回不断扩大的预算赤字并增强投资者对法国的信心，该国计划明年削减约 600 亿欧元（664 亿美元）的支出并提高税收。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/france-plans-66-billion-in-spending-cuts-and-tax-hikes-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
